article_title: HOSPITAL BOARD: Punzalan joins staff, Medicaid Expansion hopes dead for another year
article_text:
Salem, MO (65560)

Today

Scattered thunderstorms in the morning, then mainly cloudy during the afternoon with thunderstorms likely. High 83F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms developing overnight. Low 66F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.author: Tyler McConnell

og.description: Salem Memorial District Hospital Board of Directors voted Tuesday night to contract with Dr. Julius Punzalan to join SMDH Family Medicine immediately.
